    "voice_pack_intro_student": "Umunyeshuri yandika buri jwi mu ijwi rye bwite (ni byiza ku gitekerezo cyo kwiyumvamo n'imyitozo yo kuvuga). Kanda 👂 kugira ngo wumve urugero mbere, hanyuma 🎙️ kugira ngo wandike. Ijwi ry'umunyeshuri ni inyandiko ibanga: riguma kuri iki gikoresho, kandi \"Kohereza\" rikora dosiye IBANGA ugenzura.",
    "voice_pack_intro": "Andika buri jwi mu ijwi ryawe bwite: kanda 👂 kugira ngo wumve urugero, hanyuma 🎙️ uvuge ijwi mu magambo make (\"/p/\", si \"pe\"). Porogaramu icuranga ijwi ryawe mu gihe cyo kuvanga, gutandukanya n'ikarita y'ifatizo. Amajwi arimo ubusa abika ijwi risanzwe.",
    "voice_pack_consent_title": "Kwandika ijwi ry'umunyeshuri",
    "voice_pack_consent_body": "Kwandika ijwi ry'umunyeshuri ni inyandiko ibanga ifite imiterere isa na bayometiriki. Riguma kuri iki gikoresho, iki gikoresho ntirishyira kuri interineti na rimwe (igenzura rya AI, niba uricyemuye, ni cyo kintu kimwe gusa cyohereza igice hanze), kandi ushobora kurisiba igihe icyo ari cyo cyose. Emeza ko ufite uruhushya rwo kwandika uyu munyeshuri.",
