      "student_picks_a_game": "Umunyeshuri ahitamo umukino.",
      "quick_assessment": "Isuzuma ryihuse.",
      "daily_routine_templates": "⏱ Ibyitegererezo bya gahunda ya buri munsi",
      "pre_built_sequences_of_activities_that": "Inkurikirane z'ibikorwa zubatswe mbere zihuye n'ibice by'igihe bisanzwe (iminota 10, iminota 30, iminota 45). Hitamo kimwe hanyuma ukurikire.",
      "identify_fractions_2": "Menya ibice",
      "equivalent_fractions_3": "Ibice bingana",
      "compare_fractions": "Gereranya ibice",
      "add_fractions": "Ongeraho ibice",
      "multiply_fractions": "Gwiza ibice",
      "exit_ticket_generator": "🎫 Ukora itike yo gusohoka",
      "generate_a_3_question_exit_ticket_on_t": "Kora itike yo gusohoka y'ibibazo 3 ku ngingo iherutse kwigishwa. Capa hanyuma utange ku iherezo ry'isomo.",
      "topic_2": "Ingingo",
      "generate_and_print_exit_ticket": "🖨 Kora kandi ucape itike yo gusohoka",
      "grade_3_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Urutonde rwo Kugenzura Isuzuma ry'Igice ry'Umwaka wa 3",
      "grade_4_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Urutonde rwo Kugenzura Isuzuma ry'Igice ry'Umwaka wa 4",
      "grade_5_fraction_assessment_checklist": "Urutonde rwo Kugenzura Isuzuma ry'Igice ry'Umwaka wa 5",
      "assessment_checklist": "☑ Urutonde rwo kugenzura isuzuma",
      "per_grade_skills_checklists_use_during": "Inzandiko z'ubuhanga za buri mwaka. Koresha mu gihe cy'isuzuma umuntu-ku-muntu cyangwa gutegura inyigisho.",
      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Umwana wanjye avuga \"Nanga ibice\"",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "Bisanzwe cyane. Ibice bimena amategeko abanyeshuri biga ku mibare yuzuye — imibare minini ntisobanura buri gihe indangagaciro nini. Uburakari ni ubw'ukuri kandi bisanzwe. Fasha na: (1) gukoresha ibyitegererezo bigaragara nka pizza cyangwa imikanda y'igice, (2) guhuza n'ubuzima nyabwo (guteka, igihe, amafaranga), (3) kwimenyereza gato kandi kenshi (iminota 5 ku munsi) aho kuba session ndende, (4) gushimira imbaraga, atari ibisubizo byiza gusa.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Umwana wanjye ntabwo asobanukiwe IMPAMVU uburyo bukora",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "Ntabwo ari bonyine — abanyeshuri benshi biga uburyo mbere n'impamvu nyuma. Fasha ukoresheje guhora werekana uko uburyo busa n'ishusho. \"Gwiza 3/4 na 1/2\" bishobora gushushanywa nk'urukiramende. Tab ya Op Proofs ikubikorera. Baza \"kuki?\" mu bugwaneza kandi kenshi.",
      "how_can_i_help_with_homework_without_d": "Nshobora gute gufasha mu masomo yo mu rugo ntabikoreye?",
      "use_the_worked_examples_tab_they_show_": "Koresha tab ya Worked Examples — yerekana uburyo intambwe ku yindi bifite impamvu. Nyura mu bibazo bisa hamwe, atari ikimwe. Niba bavuga \"Sinzi uko natangira,\" baza \"Ni iki ikibazo gisaba ko ushaka? Ni iki tuzi?\" Sisitemu y'ibimenyetso mu Bibazo by'Amagambo itanga ibimenyetso by'urwego — gerageza icya mbere mbere y'igisubizo.",
      "what_should_i_drill": "Ni iki nkwiye kwimenyereza?",
      "ies_practice_guide_recommends_1_magnit": "IES Practice Guide isaba: (1) itekereza ry'ubunini (imirimo y'umurongo w'imibare), (2) isano hagati y'igaragara n'ikimenyetso, (3) ibibazo by'amagambo mu rwego. IRINDE: kwimenyereza ku buryo utumva. Mara iminota 5 kuri Benchmark Trainer, 5 ku Bibazo by'Amagambo, na 5 ku mukino — iyo ni session y'iminota 15 nziza.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Umwana wanjye akora uburyo neza ariko igisubizo kibi",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Akenshi bisobanura ikosa rito ry'imibare (urug., yagwije nabi) cyangwa ntiyoroshye. Werekana Cheat Sheet — bashobora kugenzura akazi kabo intambwe ku yindi. Bashishikarize kwemeza n'uburyo butandukanye (bareke bagereke mbere, cyangwa bakoreshe icyitegererezo gitandukanye).",
