      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Nzamenya nte niba umwana wanjye ari ku nzira?",
      "look_at_the_standards_tab_to_see_which": "Reba tab ya Standards kugira ngo urebe amahame ya CCSS bakwiye kumenya ku mwaka wabo. Tab ya Mastery yerekana iterambere. Ku kugenzura kwihuse: bashobora (a) gushushanya icyitegererezo cya 3/4, (b) kuvuga igice gingana na 1/2, (c) kugereranya 2/3 na 3/4 no gusobanura? Izo test eshatu zikubiyemo ibyitezwe byinshi by'igice bya K-5.",
      "parent_guide": "👨‍👩‍👧 Ubuyobozi bw'ababyeyi",
      "guidance_for_parents_helping_kids_with": "Ubuyobozi ku babyeyi bafasha abana ku bice mu rugo. Imbogamizi zisanzwe, inama zifatika, n'icyo wabaza.",
