      "the_1_2_trick": "Uburiganya bwa 1/2",
      "let_your_number_be_n_the_sequence_n_1_": "Reka umubare wawe ube n. Urukurikirane: (n+1) × 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n + 2 + 4 − 6 = 2n. Gabanya na 2 → n. Kuraho iy'umwimerere → 0. Tegereza — ibyo bitanga 0, atari 1. Gerageza: n → (n+1)×2 = 2n+2 → +4 = 2n+6 → −6 = 2n → ÷2 = n → −iy'umwimerere = 0. \"Uburiganya\" bwishingikiriza ku ma-constant yihishe mu rukurikirane.",
      "sum_of_unit_fractions": "Igiteranyo cy'ibice by'unite",
      "each_term_is_half_the_previous_the_tot": "Buri jambo ni kimwe cya kabiri cy'iryabanje. Igiteranyo cyegera 1 ariko ntikigera na rimwe. Uru ni urukurikirane rwa geometric rutagira iherezo rufite ijambo rya mbere 1/2 n'umubare 1/2: S = (1/2) / (1 − 1/2) = 1. Ni yo mpamvu paradox y'imyitozo ya Zeno ishobora gukemurwa mu mibare.",
      "the_harmonic_series": "Urukurikirane rwa harmonic",
      "even_though_each_term_is_small_the_ser": "Nubwo buri jambo ari rito, urukurikirane rurasakara. Kugira ngo urenge 100, ukeneye hafi 1.5 × 10^43 amagambo. Ibi byagaragajwe na Nicole Oresme mu myaka ya 1300 akoresheje gukusanya: 1/3 + 1/4 > 1/4 + 1/4 = 1/2; 1/5+...+1/8 > 4 × 1/8 = 1/2; ushobora buri gihe gushaka 1/2 iyindi yo kongeraho.",
      "farey_sequences": "Inkurikirane za Farey",
      "check_1_4_and_1_3_4_1_1_3_1_check_2_5_": "Reba 1/4 na 1/3: (4)(1) − (1)(3) = 1. Reba 2/5 na 1/2: (5)(1) − (2)(2) = 1. Iyi mico ikora igiti cya Stern-Brocot cy'imibare yose ya rationnel.",
      "multiplying_telescopes": "Ama-télescope yo kugwiza",
      "rewrite_1_2_2_3_3_4_n_1_n_the_2_in_2_3": "Ongera wandike: 1/2 × 2/3 × 3/4 × ... × (n−1)/n. 2 muri 2/3 isiba 2 mu mubare wo hasi wa 1/2. 3 muri 3/4 isiba 3 mu mubare wo hasi wa 2/3. Byose birasibwa uretse 1/n.",
