      "three_tools_same_denom_just_compare_to": "Ibikoresho bitatu: umubare wo hasi umwe (gereranya gusa hejuru), kugwiza-kwambukiranya (a/b na c/d → ad na bc), cyangwa benchmark na ½ / ¾. Icya nyuma ni cyihuse cyane mu mutwe wawe.",
