      "2_11_4_long_division_gives_a_terminati": "2¾ = 11/4. Kugabanya kurekurera bitanga decimal irangira (umubare wo hasi = 2¹ × 5ⁿ) cyangwa isubiramo (umubare-mbanza uwo ari wo wose mu mubare wo hasi). 1/3 = 0.333... iteka.",
