      "stack_the_fraction_wall_1_whole_2_halv": "Tumbika urukuta rw'igice: 1 cyuzuye = ibice bya kabiri 2 = ibice bya kane 4 = ibice bya munani 8. Uburebure bumwe = agaciro kamwe. Inkoni za Cuisenaire (1952) zabikoze bifatika; urukuta ni umwana wa digital.",
