      "11s_repeat_the_digit_1_9": "Imibare ya 11 isubiramo umubare (×1-9)",
      "7s_5s_2s_distributive": "7s = 5s + 2s (ikwirakwiza)",
      "pick_a_pattern_to_highlight_the_table_": "🔍 Hitamo ishusho yo kugaragaza. Imbonerahamwe yuzuyemo imiterere: igihe uyibonye, kimwe cya kabiri cy'ukuri kiba gihanurwa.",
      "multiplication_table_with_pattern_high": "Imbonerahamwe yo kugwiza ifite kugaragaza ishusho",
      "click_any_pattern_above_to_light_up_th": "👆 Kanda ishusho iyo ari yo yose hejuru kugira ngo umurikire utuyobora kandi usome amategeko. Amashusho menshi ashobora kwisumbirana (urugero, 5×5 ni «umugwizo wa 5» kandi «kare yuzuye»).",
      "why_patterns_beat_brute_memorization": "💡 Impamvu amashusho aruta kwiga ku mutwe ku gahato",
      "you_only_need_to_memorize_about_a_thir": "Ukeneye kwiga ku mutwe gusa hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'imbonerahamwe. ",
      "anything_in_the_1s_2s_5s_10s_11s_colum": "Ikintu cyose kiri mu nkingi za 1, 2, 5, 10 na 11 gifite itegeko ryoroshye. Kare ni itsinda rito (ukuri 12). Ibisigaye ni «hagati hakomeye» — hafi ukuri 15 — gusaba kwiga ku mutwe by'ukuri: 6×7, 6×8, 6×9, 7×8, 7×9, 8×9 n'impanga zabyo.",
      "distributive_shortcut_for_the_tricky_m": "Inzira ngufi y'ikwirakwiza ku hagati hakomeye. ",
      "forget_7_8_7_8_5_8_2_8_40_16_56_build_": "Wibagiwe 7×8? 7×8 = 5×8 + 2×8 = 40 + 16 = 56. Ubaka ukuri gukomeye uhereye ku byoroshye bibiri. Nyuma yo gusubiramo bihagije, igisubizo kiba cyikora.",
      "for_dyscalculia_specifically": "By'umwihariko ku ngorane zo kubara (dyscalculia): ",
      "visualizing_each_fact_as_an_area_model": "Kwerekana buri kuri nk'urukiramende rw'icyitegererezo cy'ubuso (igika cy'Ishusho) cyangwa nk'ishusho (iki gika) bikuha inzira igana ku gisubizo itagomba kwibuka byikoresha. Kwibuka kubakwa mu gihe, ariko ntibibaho gusa binyuze mu myitozo ya tekiniki.",
