      "this_ancient_rock_from_the_lunar_highl": "Iyi rutare ya kera iva mu misozi miremire y'ukwezi ifite imyaka miliyari 4.4 — hafi ya kera nk'Ukwezi ubwako. Iratubwira ko Ukwezi kwahoze gufite inyanja ya magma y'isi yose.",
      "basalt": "Basalt",
      "dark_volcanic_basalt_filled_the_moon_s": "Basalt y'ibirunga yijimye yuzuye ibibaya binini by'ingaruka by'Ukwezi maze ikora «inyanja» zijimye (maria) zigaragara ziva ku Isi. Iyi lava yaturikiye mu myaka miliyari 3-3.5 ishize.",
      "breccia": "Breccia",
      "a_jumbled_mix_of_rock_fragments_welded": "Ivanze ridasanzwe ry'uduce tw'urutare twahujwe hamwe n'ingaruka za meteorite. Ubuso bw'Ukwezi bwakubiswe mu myaka irenga miliyari 4.",
      "regolith_core": "Intima ya Regolith",
      "lunar_soil_is_ground_up_rock_from_bill": "Ubutaka bw'ukwezi ni urutare rwasekuwe ruva mu myaka miliyari z'ibitero by'udukomeza twa meteorite. Bufite n'ubuhumyi buto bw'ikirahuri n'ibimenyetso by'uduce tw'umuyaga w'izuba.",
      "orange_soil": "Ubutaka bw'Icunga",
      "apollo_17_found_orange_soil_tiny_glass": "Apollo 17 yabonye ubutaka bw'icunga — ubuhumyi buto bw'ikirahuri buva mu kuturika kw'ikirunga cya kera mu myaka miliyari 3.7 ishize. Ni kimwe mu byavumbuwe bishimishije cyane bya Apollo!",
      "kreep_basalt": "KREEP Basalt",
      "kreep_stands_for_potassium_k_rare_eart": "KREEP isobanura Potassium (K), Rare Earth Elements, na Phosphorus (P). Iyi mabuye y'agaciro yakoraniye mu bisigazwa bya nyuma by'inyanja ya magma y'ukwezi.",
      "impact_glass": "Ikirahuri cy'Ingaruka",
      "meteorite_impacts_melt_rock_into_glass": "Ingaruka za meteorite zishongesha urutare zikaba ikirahuri, kiguruka mu kirere kikamanuka nk'uduhimba duto. Bimwe bifite gaze zafashwe ziva mu kirere cya kera cy'ukwezi.",
      "genesis_rock": "Urutare rwa Genesis",
      "apollo_15_found_this_4_1_billion_year_": "Apollo 15 yabonye iyi anorthosite ifite imyaka miliyari 4.1, imwe mu mabuye ya kera cyane yigeze gukusanywa. Yafashije kwemeza inyigisho y'inyanja ya magma ku byerekeye iremwa ry'Ukwezi.",
      "the_moon_is_about_384_400_km_away_ligh": "Ukwezi kuri hafi km 384,400 — urumuri rufata amasegonda 1.3 kugira ngo rugere yo!",
