      "the_moon_s_gravity_is_1_6_of_earth_s_a": "Imbaraga rukuruzi z'Ukwezi ni 1/6 by'Isi. Umuntu upima kg 70 apima ~kg 12 gusa aho!",
      "the_sunlit_side_reaches_127_c_while_th": "Uruhande rumurikiwe n'izuba rugera kuri 127°C, mu gihe uruhande rwijimye rumanuka kugeza -173°C!",
      "12_astronauts_walked_on_the_moon_acros": "Abahanga mu kirere 12 bagendeye ku Kwezi muri Apollo 11, 12, 14, 15, 16, na 17.",
