      "retry_3d_mode": "Ongera Ugerageze Uburyo bwa 3D",
      "interactive_3d_lunar_surface_eva_use_w": "EVA ya 3D ikorana ku buso bw'ukwezi. Koresha WASD kugira ngo ugende, Space kugira ngo usimbuke mu mbaraga rukuruzi za kimwe cya gatandatu, F kugira ngo ukusanye ingero z'amabuye, n'imbeba kugira ngo urebe hirya no hino. Kusanya ingero z'ubumenyi bw'isi maze ushakashake ku buso bw'Ukwezi hafi ya module y'ukwezi.",
