      "the_apollo_lunar_surface_experiments_p": "Apollo Lunar Surface Experiments Package (ALSEP) yakoze imyaka nyuma y'uko abahanga mu kirere bagiye. Igipimo cy'umutingito cyamenye imitingito y'ukwezi n'ingaruka za meteorite kugeza 1977.",
