      "american_flag": "Ibendera ry'Amerika",
      "the_flags_on_the_moon_have_been_bleach": "Amabendera ari ku Kwezi yahindutse umweru usukuye kubera imyaka mirongo y'imirasire ya UV itamuriwe. Ibendera rya Apollo 12 ryonyine ni ryo umwotsi wa moteri washenye.",
      "seismometer": "Igipimo cy'Umutingito",
      "lunar_seismometers_detected_deep_moonq": "Ibipimo by'umutingito by'ukwezi byamenye imitingito y'ukwezi ikomeye yatewe n'imbaraga z'umuraba w'Isi ku burebure bwa km 700-1100. Ukwezi kuracyafite intima yashongeshejwe igice!",
      "laser_retroreflector": "Lazeri Retroreflector",
      "scientists_bounce_lasers_off_this_mirr": "Abahanga basubiza lazeri ku ndorerwamo iyi kugira ngo bapime intera y'Isi-Ukwezi ku kunyura kwa cm 1. Ukwezi kwimuka cm 3.8 kuva ku Isi buri mwaka.",
      "moonwalk_eva_3": "👨‍🚀 Kugenda ku Kwezi (EVA)",
