      "end_eva_return_to_lm": "⬆️ Soza EVA — Subira kuri LM",
      "animated_lunar_ascent_sequence_ascent_": "Urutonde rwo kuzamuka kw'ukwezi rufite imikorere. Icyiciro cyo kuzamuka kiguruka kiva ku Kwezi gisiga icyiciro cyo kumanuka inyuma, kizamuka kigana uruziga rw'ukwezi hejuru ya kilometero 60, hanyuma kigakora guhura-guhuza na module y'amategeko Columbia izenguruka. HUD yerekana uburebure, icyiciro, n'intera igana CSM.",
      "lunar_ascent_rendezvous": "Kuzamuka kw'Ukwezi no Guhura",
      "ascent_stage_launches_from_moon_docks_": "Icyiciro cyo kuzamuka kiguruka kiva ku Kwezi kandi gihuzwa na Columbia",
      "the_lm_s_ascent_engine_a_single_start_": "Moteri yo kuzamuka ya LM — moteri ya hypergolic yo gutangira rimwe idafite uburyo bwo guhagarika — itwika kugira ngo ikohereze uva ku buso bw'ukwezi. Icyiciro cyo kumanuka gikora nk'ikibanza cyo kohereza kandi gisigara inyuma. Uhura kandi uhuzwa na Columbia, hanyuma ujugunya «Eagle» (iyo amaherezo igwa ku Kwezi).",
