      "animated_re_entry_sequence_command_mod": "Urutonde rwo kongera kwinjira rufite imikorere. Module y'amategeko yinjira mu kirere kuri km 39,900/isaha hamwe n'ubushyuhe bwa plasma bugera kuri dogere 2,760. Yerekana ihagarara ry'amaradiyo, parashuti zo mbere, parashuti nkuru, no kumanuka mu mazi y'inyanja.",
