      "critical_rest_stop_after_the_500_mile_": "Ahantu ho kuruhukira h'ingenzi nyuma yo kwambuka Ikigobe cya Mexico cya kilometero 500",
      "platte_river_ne": "Platte River, NE",
      "600_000_sandhill_cranes_gather_here_ea": "Sandhill Cranes 600,000 zikoranira hano buri gihe cy'impeshyi — kimwe mu bintu byiza cyane byo kureba by'ibidukikije",
      "great_salt_lake": "Great Salt Lake",
      "5_million_migratory_birds_depend_on_th": "Inyoni zimuka miliyoni 5 zishingira kuri iyi nyanja yo mu gihugu nk'ahantu ho kongera lisansi",
      "mississippi_delta": "Delta ya Mississippi",
      "wetlands_here_support_40_of_north_amer": "Ibishanga hano bishyigikira 40% by'inyoni z'amazi zimuka za Amerika y'Amajyaruguru",
      "chesapeake_bay": "Chesapeake Bay",
      "largest_estuary_in_the_us_critical_win": "Estuwari nini kurusha izindi muri US — ahantu h'ingenzi ho gutura mu gihe cy'itumba ku mbata n'inzuzi",
