      "distance": "Intera",
      "speed": "Umuvuduko",
      "altitude": "Uburebure",
      "formation": "Imiterere",
      "fun_fact": "Ukuri Gushimishije: ",
      "the_four_north_american_flyways": "🗺️ Inzira Enye zo Kuguruka za Amerika y'Amajyaruguru",
      "atlantic_2": "Atlantike",
      "mississippi_2": "Mississippi",
      "central_2": "Hagati",
      "pacific_2": "Pasifike",
      "when_do_birds_migrate": "📅 Ni Ryari Inyoni Zimuka?",
      "migration_timing_varies_dramatically_b": "Igihe cyo kwimuka gitandukanye cyane bitewe n'ubwoko:",
      "early_spring_waterfowl_ducks_geese_hea": "Intangiriro y'impeshyi: Inyoni z'amazi (imbata, inzuzi) zerekeza mu majyaruguru zikurikira gushonga kw'urubura. Red-winged Blackbirds zisubira mu bishanga.",
      "peak_spring_warblers_vireos_tanagers_f": "Impinga y'impeshyi: Warblers, vireos na tanagers zuzuza amajyaruguru. Inyoni nyinshi ziririmba zimuka nijoro. Ku majoro yo hejuru harimo inyoni zirenga miliyoni 500 mu kirere.",
      "shorebirds_start_south_some_species_fa": "Inyoni zo ku nkombe zitangira mu majyepfo — ubwoko bumwe “burananirwa” ahantu ho kororokera bugatangira gusubira mu ntangiriro ya Nyakanga. Abakuru akenshi bagenda mbere y'ibyana.",
      "peak_fall_raptors_ride_thermals_along_": "Impinga y'itumba: Inyamanswa ziguruka hejuru y'imigezi y'ubushyuhe hafi y'imisozi. Inyoni ziririmba zerekeza mu majyepfo zikurikira imbere z'ubukonje. Inzuzi ziguruka mu miterere ya V nijoro.",
      "photoperiod_day_length_is_the_primary_": "Uburebure bw'umunsi ni impamvu y'ibanze yo kwimuka. Uko iminsi igabanuka mu itumba, hormone zitera “Zugunruhe” — kutaruhuka kwo kwimuka — kandi inyoni zitangira gukusanya ububiko bw'ibinure (kurya birenze), rimwe na rimwe zibyaza kabiri ibiro by'umubiri.",
      "stopover_ecology": "⛺ Ubumenyi bw'Ibinyabuzima bw'Ahantu ho Guhagarara",
      "stopovers_are_not_just_rest_stops_they": "Ahantu ho guhagarara si ahantu ho kuruhuka gusa, ni ",
      "refueling_stations": "ahantu ho kongera lisansi",
      "critical_to_survival_a_migrating_warbl": " h'ingenzi mu kubaho. Warbler yimuka ishobora gukoresha 75% by'igihe cyo kwimuka ku hantu ho guhagarara, irya cyane kugira ngo yubake ububiko bw'ibinure. Ahantu ho gutura ho guhagarara ho kwiza hashobora kuba itandukaniro riri hagati y'ubuzima n'urupfu.",
      "at_delaware_bay_over_1_million_shorebi": "Kuri Delaware Bay, inyoni zo ku nkombe zirenga miliyoni 1 (Red Knots, Ruddy Turnstones, Sanderlings) zishingira ku magi y'inkona y'ifarasi yateweho muri Gicurasi. Igihe kigomba kuba cyiza rwose: inyoni zigera igihe nyacyo inkona z'ifarasi zibika amagi. Niba umubare w'inkona z'ifarasi ugabanutse (kubera uburobyi burenze bw'inyoni), urunigi rwose rwo kwimuka rurasenyuka.",
      "conservation_success_story_after_horse": "Inkuru y'intsinzi yo kubungabunga: Nyuma yo gushyiraho imipaka yo gusarura inkona z'ifarasi mu 2012, umubare wa Red Knot watangiye gukira buhoro buhoro uva ku rwego rwo hasi rw'ihindagurika rwa 15,000 kugera birenze 50,000 muri 2025.",
      "migration_physiology": "🦴 Fiziyolojiya yo Kwimuka",
      "migration_is_one_of_the_most_physicall": "Kwimuka ni kimwe mu bikorwa bisaba umubiri cyane mu bwami bw'inyamaswa. Inyoni zinyuramo impinduka z'umubiri zitangaje mbere yo kugenda:",
      "hyperphagia": "Kurya Birenze",
      "before_migration_birds_enter_a_feeding": "Mbere yo kwimuka, inyoni zinjira mu kurya birenze byitwa hyperphagia, zirya ku muvuduko w'inshuro 2-3 kurusha ibisanzwe. Blackpoll Warbler (garamu 12) yongeraho ububiko bw'ibinure bwa garamu 8-12, hafi ibyaza kabiri ibiro by'umubiri. Aya binure ni lisansi y'indege zidahagarara zirenga kilometero 2,000.",
      "organ_shrinkage": "Kugabanuka kw'Ingingo",
      "to_reduce_weight_migrating_birds_actua": "Kugira ngo zigabanye ibiro, inyoni zimuka zigabanya rwose ingingo zicira (amara, umwijima, igifu) kugera 40% mbere yo kugenda. Iyo zigeze ku hantu ho guhagarara, zongera kubaka izi ngingo vuba kugira ngo zongere lisansi. Iyi “plastiki ya fenotipe” ni iyihariye mu nyamaswa zifite uruti rw'umugongo.",
      "hemoglobin": "Hemoglobine",
      "high_altitude_migrants_like_bar_headed": "Abimuka b'uburebure bwo hejuru nka Bar-headed Geese (ziguruka metero 29,000 hejuru ya Himalaya) bafite hemoglobine yihariye ifite ikurura rinini rya ogisijeni. Imikaya yabo irimo myoglobine y'inyongera, kandi ubwinshi bwa kapilari yabo ni kabiri bw'ubwoko bwo hasi.",
      "sleep_in_flight": "Gusinzira mu Ndege",
      "some_birds_can_sleep_while_flying_usin": "Inyoni zimwe zishobora gusinzira mu gihe ziguruka, zikoresha “ibitotsi by'igice cy'ubwonko” — zifunga igice kimwe cy'ubwonko icyarimwe. Frigatebirds zanditswe zisinzira iminota 42 ku munsi mu gihe cy'indege z'iminsi 10 zambuka inyanja, zifata ibitotsi bito bya segonda 12 buri kimwe.",
      "navigation_clock": "Isaha yo Kuyobora",
      "birds_maintain_an_internal_circadian_c": "Inyoni zigumana isaha ya circadian yo imbere ifite ukuri gutangaje. Iyi saha yishyura imigendere y'izuba mu kirere (busole y'izuba yishyuwe igihe) kandi ikurikirana impinduka z'ibihe z'uburebure bw'umunsi zitera hormone zo kwimuka.",
      "zugunruhe": "Zugunruhe",
      "zugunruhe_migration_restlessness_is_a_": "Zugunruhe (“kutaruhuka kwo kwimuka”) ni imiterere y'imyitwarire aho inyoni zimuka zafunzwe mu kigo zikubita amababa mu cyerekezo zaba zimuka mu buryo busanzwe, mu gihe zaba zimuka. Iterwa na hormone kandi yanditswe muri gene. N'inyoni zarezwe n'intoki zidafite uburambe bwo kwimuka zerekana Zugunruhe.",
      "species_comparison": "📊 Kugereranya Ubwoko",
      "canada_goose": "Canada Goose",
      "3_000_ft": "metero 3,000",
      "arctic_tern": "Arctic Tern",
      "1_500_ft": "metero 1,500",
