      "use_apps_like_ebird_cornell_lab_to_rep": "Koresha porogaramu nka eBird (Cornell Lab) kugira ngo utange raporo yo kwitegereza inyoni. Amakuru yawe afasha abahanga gukurikirana igihe cyo kwimuka n'ibigenda by'umubare.",
