      "are_in_the_air_over_north_america_simu": " ziba mu kirere hejuru ya Amerika y'Amajyaruguru icyarimwe. Sitasiyo za radar y'ikirere zimenya ibicu binini by'inyoni zimuka ziguruka izuba rirenga. Ushobora kureba kwimuka mu gihe nyacyo kuri BirdCast (birdcast.info).",
      "most_songbird_migration_happens_at_nig": "Kwimuka kwinshi kw'inyoni ziririmba kubera nijoro, iyo umuyaga utuje, inyamanswa ari nkeya, kandi inyenyeri zigaragara mu kuyobora. Inyoni zikoresha ",
