      "magnetic_sense": "Kumva rukuruzi",
      "of_birds_may_work_through_quantum_mech": " kw'inyoni bishobora gukora binyuze mu mekanike ya quantum. Poroteyine za cryptochrome mu maso y'inyoni zishobora gukoresha ihuriro rya quantum kugira ngo zimenye umurima wa rukuruzi w'Isi — bituma kuyobora kw'inyoni kuba kimwe mu bikorwa bike by'ibinyabuzima bishingira kuri fiziki ya quantum.",
