      "polarization_pattern": "uburyo bwa polarizasiyo",
      "of_sunlight_even_through_heavy_cloud_c": " bw'urumuri rw'izuba ndetse no binyuze mu bicu biremereye, bikoresha ba-cône bihariye byumva UV muri retine yabo. Ibi bisobanura ndetse no ku minsi y'ibicu inyoni zishobora kumenya ahantu h'izuba kandi zikagumana inzira yazo.",
