      "explain_in_your_own_words": "Sobanura mu magambo yawe bwite...",
      "inquiry_widget_no_score_no_reveal_no_a": "Widget y'iperereza — nta amanota, nta kugaragaza, nta mwuzure w'ibisubizo. Icyitegererezo cy'ingufu ni icy'urugero (gukurura ∝ m^0.67 / ubugari bw'ijaba). Kubika kw'imiterere ya V bitandukanye ~10 kugeza 30% bitewe n'ubwoko n'ahantu (Lissaman & Shollenberger 1970, umupaka wo hejuru w'inyigisho; ibipimo mu ndege birimo Weimerskirch et al. 2001 ku bapelikani na Portugal et al. 2014 ku ba-ibis). Widget ikoresha 22% nk'igereranyo cyo hagati. Ku bijyanye n'ubumenyi bw'ibinyabuzima nyabwo bw'ahantu ho guhagarara, reba ibitabo by'ibanze.",
