      "migration_routes_flyways": "Inzira zo Kwimuka + Inzira zo Kuguruka",
      "four_major_north_american_flyways_paci": "Inzira enye nkuru zo kuguruka za Amerika y'Amajyaruguru (Pasifike, Hagati, Mississippi, Atlantike) ziyobora miliyari z'inyoni inshuro ebyiri ku mwaka. Maine iri ku mutwe w'inzira yo kuguruka ya Atlantike.",
      "aerodynamics_of_bird_flight": "Ubumenyi bw'Imigendere y'Umwuka bw'Indege y'Inyoni",
      "wing_shape_aspect_ratio_camber_tunes_l": "Imiterere y'ijaba (igipimo cy'imiterere + kugoramuka) ihuza kuzamura ku gukurura. Inyoni ziguruka = igipimo cy'imiterere cyo hejuru, gukubita ijaba gahoro. Ba-hummingbird = igipimo cy'imiterere cyo hasi, gukubita ijaba birenga 60 Hz.",
