      "stable_for_10_000_years_holocene_clima": "Bihamye imyaka 10,000. Ikirere cya Holocène aho umuco wose w'abantu wakuriye.",
      "keeling_starts_measuring_1958": "Keeling atangira gupima (1958)",
      "charles_david_keeling_begins_continuou": "Charles David Keeling atangira gukurikirana CO₂ ku buryo buhoraho i Mauna Loa. Umurongo we wagaragaje ko ubushyuhe buterwa n'abantu ari ukuri.",
      "350_ppm_1988": "350 ppm (1988)",
      "climate_scientist_james_hansen_tells_u": "Umuhanga w'ikirere James Hansen abwira Kongere ya Amerika ko ubushyuhe bwatangiye. 350.org ifata 350 ppm nk'urubibi “rutekanye”.",
      "400_ppm_2013": "400 ppm (2013)",
      "first_time_atmospheric_co_crossed_400_": "Ubwa mbere CO₂ yo mu kirere yarengeje 400 ppm mu myaka miliyoni 3+. Igihe cya nyuma cya 400 ppm cy'Isi: amashyamba y'ubushyuhe ku mpera z'isi.",
      "420_ppm_2023": "420 ppm (2023)",
      "current_level_highest_in_at_least_800_": "Urwego rwa none. Rwo hejuru cyane mu byibura imyaka 800,000 (biva mu bikonje). Bingana na ~1.2°C by'ubushyuhe.",
      "450_ppm_projected_2035": "450 ppm (biteganyijwe ~2035)",
      "threshold_associated_with_2_c_warming_": "Urubibi rufitanye isano n'ubushyuhe bwa 2°C nibikomeza. Intego y'Amasezerano ya Paris: kuguma munsi ya 1.5°C.",
      "tropical_coral_reef_die_off": "Gupfa kw'Amabuye ya Korali y'Ubushyuhe",
      "mass_coral_bleaching_events_hit_the_gr": "Ibintu byinshi byo kwera kwa korali byakubise Great Barrier Reef mu 2016, 2017, 2020, 2022, na 2024. Ku bushyuhe bwa 1.5°C, 70–90% by'amabuye ya korali y'ubushyuhe arapfa. Kuri 2°C, 99% arapfa.",
      "greenland_ice_sheet_collapse": "Guhirima kw'Urubura rwa Greenland",
      "the_greenland_ice_sheet_holds_enough_w": "Urubura rwa Greenland rufite amazi ahagije yo kuzamura urwego rw'inyanja metero 7 (23 ft). Ku ~1.5°C bikomeje, gushonga bihinduka ikitagaruka mu binyejana kugeza ku bihumbi by'imyaka.",
      "amoc_collapse_gulf_stream": "Guhirima kwa AMOC (Gulf Stream)",
      "the_atlantic_meridional_overturning_ci": "Uruziga rwa AMOC rutwara ubushyuhe ruva mu turere dushyushye rukajya Uburayi. Rwagabanutse 15% kuva 1950. Guhagarara burundu byakonjesha Uburayi bw'amajyaruguru cyane bikanabangamira imvura ya monsoon muri Afurika na Aziya.",
      "amazon_rainforest_dieback": "Kugabanuka kw'Ishyamba ry'Imvura rya Amazon",
      "the_amazon_generates_half_its_own_rain": "Amazon itanga kimwe cya kabiri cy'imvura yayo. Hamwe no gutema amashyamba 20–25% + ubushyuhe buzamuka, ifite ibyago byo guhinduka iva ku ishyamba ry'imvura ikajya ku isambu. Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwerekana ko urubibi rwegereye 2°C ku gipimo cyo gutema cy'ubu.",
      "permafrost_methane_release": "Gusohora Methane kwa Permafrost",
      "arctic_permafrost_holds_twice_the_carb": "Permafrost ya Arctique ifite karubone incuro ebyiri z'iri mu kirere ubu. Ishyuha 3–4× vuba kuruta impuzandengo y'isi, isanzwe irashonga ikanasohora CO₂ na methane (bikomeye 28× kuruta CO₂ mu myaka 100).",
      "west_antarctic_ice_sheet": "Urubura rw'Antarctique y'Uburengerazuba",
      "marine_based_ice_sheets_anchored_below": "Urubura rushingiye ku nyanja rwakomejwe munsi y'urwego rw'inyanja. Amazi ashyushye y'inyanja arayarigata avuye hasi. Urubura rwa Thwaites (“Doomsday Glacier”) ni cyo cyago nyamukuru. Guhirima bizazamura urwego rw'inyanja metero 3.3 (11 ft).",
      "boreal_forest_die_off": "Gupfa kw'Ishyamba rya Boréal",
      "northern_coniferous_forests_russia_can": "Amashyamba y'amajyaruguru y'ibihuru (Uburusiya, Kanada, Scandinavia) ari mu mihangayiko iterwa n'ubushyuhe, udukoko tw'ibishishwa, n'inkongi z'amashyamba. Guhinduka burundu bikaba ubwatsi bishobora gusohora karubone nyinshi cyane yabitswe.",
      "gulf_of_maine_rapid_warming": "Ubushyuhe Bwihuse bwa Gulf of Maine",
      "the_gulf_of_maine_has_warmed_faster_th": "Gulf of Maine yashyushye vuba kuruta 99% by'inyanja z'isi kuva 1980 — hafi 0.5°F kuri buri myaka icumi, hafi 3× impuzandengo y'inyanja ku isi. Umuyaga ukonje wa Labrador wagabanutse mu gihe amazi ashyushye ya Gulf Stream ageze mu majyaruguru cyane, ari kuvugurura urusobe rw'ibiribwa mu gihe nyacyo kuva ku shingiro. Imiryango yo ku nkombe ya Penobscot, Passamaquoddy, Maliseet, na Mi’kmaq bari barandika iyi mihindagurikire mu nyandiko z'akanwa mu myaka mirongo mbere y'uko satelite zibyemeza.",
      "onshore_wind_turbines": "Turbine z'Umuyaga zo ku Butaka",
      "cheapest_electricity_worldwide_in_2024": "Amashanyarazi ahenze gake ku isi mu 2024. Ubushobozi bwikuba kabiri buri mwaka mu turere twinshi.",
      "utility_scale_solar_farms": "Imirima y'Izuba y'Urwego rwa Serivisi",
      "cheapest_electricity_in_history_grid_i": "Amashanyarazi ahenze gake mu mateka. Guhuza urusobe ni cyo kibazo nyamukuru ubu.",
      "rooftop_solar": "Izuba ryo ku Gisenge",
      "distributed_resilient_typical_5kw_syst": "Byatataniye + bikomeye. Kugarura amafaranga ya sisitemu isanzwe ya 5kW: imyaka 6–10.",
      "reduced_food_waste": "Kugabanya Gutakaza Ibiryo",
      "1_3_of_food_is_wasted_preventing_waste": "1/3 by'ibiryo birapfa ubusa. Kubuza gutakaza birinda methane iva mu irunda KANDI isohoka ryo guhinga ibiryo.",
      "plant_rich_diets": "Imirire Ikungahaye ku Bimera",
      "not_100_vegan_even_cutting_beef_3_a_we": "Ntabwo ari 100% vegan — no kugabanya inyama y'inka 3× mu cyumweru bifite ingaruka nini. Birekura ubutaka bwo kongera guteramo amashyamba.",
      "tropical_forest_restoration": "Kuvugurura Ishyamba ry'Ubushyuhe",
