      "206_bones_support_protection_movement_": "Amagufa 206 — gushyigikira, kurinda, kwimuka, kubika amabuye y'agaciro, gukora amaraso.",
      "houses_meninges_brain_and_cranial_nerv": "Irimo meninges, ubwonko, n'utwobo tw'imyakura y'igihanga. Imisono (coronal, sagittal, lambdoid) irahurira igihe umwana agize imyaka 2.",
      "ribs_1_12": "Imbavu (1-12)",
      "hyoid_bone": "Igufwa rya Hyoid",
      "atlas_c1_axis_c2": "Atlas (C1) na Axis (C2)",
