      "pelvic_floor_levator_ani": "Hasi y'urubavu (Levator Ani)",
      "diaphragm_muscle": "Diaphragm (Umutsi)",
      "heart_60_000_miles_of_vessels_5l_of_bl": "Umutima, kilometero 60,000 z'imitsi, litiro 5 z'amaraso — utanga O₂, intungamubiri, hormone; ukuraho imyanda.",
      "circle_of_willis": "Circle of Willis",
      "great_saphenous_vein": "Umutsi Munini wa Saphenous",
      "lymphatic_vessels": "Imitsi ya Lymph",
      "cns_brain_spinal_cord_and_pns_31_spina": "CNS (ubwonko + uruti rw'umugongo) na PNS (amakipe 31 y'imyakura y'umugongo, amakipe 12 y'imyakura y'igihanga, sisitemu y'imyakura yigenga).",
      "lightest_sleep_transition_from_wakeful": "Ibitotsi byoroshye cyane — guhinduka uva mu kuba maso. Kunyeganyega gahoro kw'amaso, imbaraga z'imitsi zigabanuka. Guhinda kwa hypnic (kunyeganyega kwa myoclonic) birasanzwe. Byoroshye gukanguka. Imiraba ya vertex ikarishye igaragara kuri EEG.",
      "true_sleep_begins_core_body_temperatur": "Ibitotsi nyabyo bitangira. Ubushyuhe bwo hagati bw'umubiri buragabanuka, imikubitire y'umutima igabanuka. Sleep spindles (guturika kwa thalamocortical) birinda ibitotsi kandi bikahamya kwibuka kwo kwimuka. K-complexes ni imiraba minini yitabira ibimenyetso byo hanze.",
      "deep_slow_wave_sleep_sws_most_restorat": "Ibitotsi byimbitse/by'umuraba gahoro (SWS). Icyiciro gisubiza imbaraga cyane. Gusohora hormone y'imikurire bigera hejuru. Sisitemu ya glymphatic isukura imyanda y'ubwonko (amyloid-β). Guhamya kwibuka gutangaza biba. Bigoye cyane gukanguka; ubunebwe bw'ibitotsi iyo ukanguwe.",
      "dreaming_stage_brain_is_highly_active_": "Icyiciro cy'inzozi. Ubwonko burakora cyane (nk'ukuba maso) ariko umubiri urakumira (atonia binyuze mu kubuza kw'igihuru cy'ubwonko imyakura yo kwimuka). Kunyeganyega vuba kw'amaso guhuza. Gutunganya kwibuka kw'amarangamutima no gukemura ibibazo mu buhanga. Ibihe birekurura mu ijoro.",
      "cerebral_cortex_4_lobes": "Igikonoshwa cy'Ubwonko (Ibice 4)",
      "brodmann_areas_map_52_cytoarchitectura": "Uturere twa Brodmann tugaragaza uturere 52 tw'imiterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo. Igikonoshwa cy'ibanze cyo kwimuka (agace 4), igikonoshwa cy'ibanze cy'ibyiyumviro by'umubiri (utuce 3,1,2), igikonoshwa cy'ibanze cyo kubona (agace 17), igikonoshwa cy'ibanze cyo kumva (utuce 41,42). Igikonoshwa cya prefrontal ni cyo cya nyuma kubona myelin (~imyaka 25).",
      "purkinje_cells_are_among_the_largest_n": "Ingirabuzimafatizo za Purkinje ziri mu myakura minini cyane, buri imwe yakira nka 200,000 z'inyunge za synaptic. Igikonoshwa cya cerebellar gifite ibyiciro 3: molecular, Purkinje, granular. Ubushakashatsi bushya bwerekana uruhare rwabyo mu kumva, amarangamutima, n'ururimi.",
      "brainstem_midbrain_pons_medulla": "Igihuru cy'Ubwonko (Ubwonko bwo Hagati, Pons, Medulla)",
      "contains_nuclei_for_cranial_nerves_iii": "Kirimo nuclei z'imyakura y'igihanga III–XII. Sisitemu ya reticular activating (RAS) ni \"buto yo gucana\" y'ubwonko — kwangirika bitera koma. Kwambuka kwa piramide muri medulla: kwambuka kwo kwimuka bisobanura kugenzura kwo kwimuka kw'uruhande runyuranye.",
      "memory_replay_during_sleep_hippocampal": "Gusubiramo kwibuka mu gihe cy'ibitotsi: imyakura ya hippocampal \"isubiramo\" ibyabaye ku manywa mu bitotsi bya N3, yimura kwibuka kuri neocortex. Ingirabuzimafatizo za grid mu gikonoshwa cya entorhinal zitanga ibipimo by'umwanya ku ngirabuzimafatizo z'ahantu za hippocampal.",
      "fear_conditioning_pathway_auditory_cor": "Inzira yo kwigisha ubwoba: igikonoshwa cyo kumva → amygdala y'uruhande → amygdala yo hagati → hypothalamus (igisubizo cy'umuhangayiko) + PAG (guhagarara). Imikoranire ya amygdala-prefrontal itanga uburyo bwo kugenzura amarangamutima — urufatiro rw'ubuvuzi bwa CBT.",
      "key_nuclei_vpl_vpm_somatosensory_relay": "Nuclei z'ingenzi: VPL/VPM (koherereza ibyiyumviro by'umubiri), LGN (koherereza kubona kuri V1), MGN (koherereza kumva kuri A1), pulvinar (kwitondera), itsinda rya nuclei ryo imbere (kwibuka, uruziga rwa Papez).",
      "thermostat_analogy_anterior_hypothalam": "Ingero ya thermostat: hypothalamus yo imbere itera gukonja (kwaguka kw'imitsi, kubira ibyuya); hypothalamus yo inyuma itera gushyuha (guhinda umushyitsi, guhina imitsi). Umuriro = urwego rwazamuwe na prostaglandins ziturutse ku ndwara.",
      "split_brain_experiments_revealed_hemis": "Ubushakashatsi bwo kugabanya ubwonko bwagaragaje ubuhanga bw'ibice: uruhande rw'ibumoso = ururimi, ubwenge; uruhande rw'iburyo = gutunganya umwanya, byuzuye. Amakuru atangwa ku murima umwe wo kubona atunganywa n'uruhande runyuranye.",
      "dopamine_from_substantia_nigra_modulat": "Dopamine iva muri substantia nigra igenzura inzira ziziguye (D1, ihagurutsa) n'izitaziguye (D2, ibuza). Gutakaza iki kugenzura muri Parkinson bitera ingorane zihariye zo gutangira kwimuka.",
      "cranial_nerves_i_xii": "Imyakura y'Igihanga (I-XII)",
      "returns_interstitial_fluid_absorbs_die": "Isubiza amazi yo hagati y'ingirabuzimafatizo, inyunyuza ibinure by'ibiryo, kurinda umubiri — utubunda twa lymph 600–700, thymus, spleen.",
      "major_visceral_organs_respiration_dige": "Ingingo nkuru zo mu nda — guhumeka, kugogora, gutunganya, kugenzura endocrine.",
      "integumentary": "Uruhu",
      "skin_largest_organ_2m_hair_nails_gland": "Uruhu (ingingo nini kurusha izindi, ~2m²), umusatsi, inzara, glande — inzitizi, kugenzura ubushyuhe, kumva, gukora vitamine D.",
