      "gas_exchange": "Guhererekanya Gaze",
      "the_circulatory_system_delivers_deoxyg": "Sisitemu y'amaraso itwara amaraso adafite ogisijeni ku bihaha, aho sisitemu yo guhumeka iyuzuza ogisijeni ikanakuraho karuboni dioside binyuze mu ruhu ruto rwa alveoli-capillary.",
      "neuromuscular_junction": "Aho Umwakura n'Umutsi Bihurira",
      "motor_neurons_from_the_nervous_system_": "Imyakura yo kwimuka iva muri sisitemu y'imyakura isohora acetylcholine aho umwakura n'umutsi bihurira, itera guhina kw'ubwoya bw'umutsi. Nta bimenyetso by'imyakura, imitsi ntishobora kwimuka.",
      "lever_system_for_movement": "Sisitemu ya Levier yo Kwimuka",
      "muscles_attach_to_bones_via_tendons_an": "Imitsi ifatana n'amagufa binyuze mu misumari kandi ikurura ku ngingo, ikora sisitemu za levier. Urwungano rw'amagufa rutanga levier zikomeye; imitsi itanga imbaraga zo gukurura.",
      "hormonal_regulation_of_reproduction": "Kugenzura kwa Hormone kwo Kubyara",
      "the_hypothalamus_pituitary_axis_releas": "Umurongo wa hypothalamus-pituitary usohora FSH na LH bigenzura ingingo z'imyororokere. Estrogen, progesterone, na testosterone biva mu ngingo z'imyororokere bisubiza igisubizo kuri sisitemu ya endocrine.",
      "immune_defense_and_fluid_balance": "Kurinda Umubiri no Kuringaniza Amazi",
      "the_lymphatic_system_returns_interstit": "Sisitemu ya lymph isubiza amazi yo hagati y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu maraso kandi yohereza ingirabuzimafatizo zirinda umubiri zakorewe mu ngingo za lymph. Sisitemu zombi zibungabunga homeostasis y'amazi kandi zirwanya indwara.",
      "hypothalamic_pituitary_axis_2": "Umurongo wa Hypothalamic-Pituitary",
      "the_hypothalamus_bridges_the_nervous_a": "Hypothalamus ihuza sisitemu y'imyakura na endocrine — ihuza ibimenyetso by'imyakura ikabihindura amabwiriza ya hormone agenzura glande ya pituitary n'urukurikirane rwose rwa hormone ruri munsi yayo.",
      "breathing_mechanics": "Uburyo bwo Guhumeka",
      "the_diaphragm_and_intercostal_muscles_": "Diaphragm n'imitsi yo hagati y'imbavu byaguka bikanahina umwobo w'igituza mu buryo bw'umubiri kugira ngo byimure umwuka. Ibihaha ntibifite umutsi wabyo bwite kandi byishingikiriza rwose ku mitsi ikikije.",
      "sensory_receptors_in_skin": "Ibyakira Ibyiyumviro mu Ruhu",
      "the_skin_contains_millions_of_speciali": "Uruhu rurimo miliyoni z'impera z'imyakura zihariye n'ibyakira bipfundikijwe bimenya gukorwaho, igitutu, ubushyuhe, n'ububabare, bihora bitanga amakuru y'ibyiyumviro kuri sisitemu y'imyakura.",
      "portal_circulation_and_nutrient_proces": "Amaraso ya Portal no Gutunganya Intungamubiri",
      "blood_from_the_gi_tract_drains_through": "Amaraso ava mu muyoboro wa GI atemba binyuze mu mutsi wa hepatic portal aca ku mwijima mbere yo kwinjira mu maraso rusange, bituma umwijima utunganya intungamubiri mbere kandi ukavana uburozi.",
      "bone_marrow_blood_cell_production": "Gukora Ingirabuzimafatizo z'Amaraso mu Musokoro w'Igufwa",
      "red_bone_marrow_inside_the_skeleton_is": "Umusokoro utukura w'igufwa uri mu rwungano rw'amagufa ni aho havukira ingirabuzimafatizo zose z'amaraso. Ingirabuzimafatizo zitukura z'amaraso, ingirabuzimafatizo zera z'amaraso, na plaquettes zose zikorerwa hano binyuze mu gukora amaraso.",
