      "which_structure_is_most_likely_affecte": "Ni iyihe miterere ishoboka cyane kwibasirwa?",
      "patella_patellofemoral_joint": "Igufwa ry'ivi / ingingo ya patellofemoral",
      "patellofemoral_pain_syndrome_occurs_wh": "Indwara y'ububabare bwa patellofemoral iba iyo igufwa ry'ivi ridatembera neza mu muferege waryo ku gufwa ry'itako. Igitutu gisubiramo kiva mu kwiruka gitera kubabara kwa cartilage. Ubuvuzi burimo gukomeza quad, guhamya urukiro, no guhindura ibikorwa.",
      "the_shoulder_that_won_t_lift": "Ipfundo Ritazamuka",
      "which_structure_is_most_likely_torn": "Ni iyihe miterere ishoboka cyane gutabuka?",
      "supraspinatus_tendon_rotator_cuff": "Umusumari wa supraspinatus (rotator cuff)",
      "the_supraspinatus_is_the_most_commonly": "Supraspinatus ni umutsi wa rotator cuff utabuka cyane. Unyura munsi ya acromion aho uhura n'igitutu no gutabuka. Akazi ko hejuru y'umutwe nko gusiga irangi kongera iki kaga cyane.",
      "racing_heart_after_exercise": "Umutima Ukubita Vuba Nyuma yo Kwimenyereza Umubiri",
      "which_structure_controls_the_normal_he": "Ni iyihe miterere igenzura imikubitire isanzwe y'umutima?",
      "sinoatrial_sa_node": "Sinoatrial (SA) node",
      "the_sa_node_in_the_right_atrium_is_the": "SA node iri mu atrium y'iburyo ni pacemaker karemano y'umutima. Mu gihe cyo kwimenyereza umubiri gukomeye, adrenaline ishobora gutera imikubitire itagira ingaruka mbi mu gihe imikubitire y'umutima ihindagurika. Arrhythmias zikomeza zigomba gusuzumwa kugira ngo hakurweho indwara y'umutima y'imiterere.",
      "the_numb_hand": "Ukuboko Kwapfuye",
      "which_nerve_is_being_compressed": "Ni uwuhe mwakura ukandamizwa?",
      "median_nerve_carpal_tunnel_syndrome": "Umwakura wa median (indwara ya carpal tunnel)",
      "carpal_tunnel_syndrome_is_compression_": "Indwara ya carpal tunnel ni ukwandamizwa kw'umwakura wa median munsi ya flexor retinaculum ku ijoro ry'ukuboko. Umwakura wa median utanga ibyiyumviro ku rutoki runini n'intoki 3.5 za mbere. Gukoresha ijoro ry'ukuboko kenshi ni impamvu ikomeye y'akaga.",
      "the_swollen_neck_node": "Akabunda k'Ijosi Kabyimbye",
      "what_diagnosis_must_be_urgently_ruled_": "Ni iyihe ndwara igomba gukurwaho byihutirwa?",
      "lymphoma_hodgkin_lymphoma": "Lymphoma (Hodgkin lymphoma)",
      "painless_lymphadenopathy_with_b_sympto": "Kubyimba kw'utubunda twa lymph bidababaza, hamwe n'ibimenyetso bya B (ibyuya by'ijoro, gutakaza ibiro, umuriro) ni ikimenyetso gisanzwe cya Hodgkin lymphoma ku basore. Biopsy yerekana ingirabuzimafatizo za Reed-Sternberg yemeza isuzuma.",
      "the_diabetic_emergency": "Ihutirwa rya Diyabete",
      "which_cells_failed_and_what_is_the_eme": "Ni izihe ngirabuzimafatizo zananiwe, kandi ni iyihe mimerere y'ihutirwa?",
      "beta_cells_of_islets_of_langerhans_dia": "Ingirabuzimafatizo beta za islets of Langerhans; Diabetic Ketoacidosis (DKA)",
