      "bronchi": "Bronchi",
      "the_trachea_splits_into_left_and_right": "Umuyoboro w'umwuka ugabanyamo bronchi nkuru z'ibumoso n'iz'iburyo, buri imwe yinjira mu ihaha rimwe. Zigabanyamo bronchioles nto.",
