      "jejunum_ileum": "Jéjunum na Iléum",
      "most_nutrient_absorption_occurs_here_v": "Kunyunyuza intungamubiri kwinshi biba hano binyuze muri villi na microvilli, byongera ubuso inshuro 600. Uburebure bwa metero 6-7.",
