      "dna_genetics_lab": "🧬 DNA / Laboratwari ya Genetics",
      "build_replicate_transcribe_translate_m": "Ubaka • Gukoporora • Kwandika • Guhindura • Guhinduka • CRISPR • Siyansi y'ubutabera",
      "build_the_double_helix_from_4_letters": "Ubaka double helix uhereye ku nyuguti 4",
      "a_pairs_with_t_2_bonds_g_with_c_3_wats": "A ihuza na T (bond 2), G na C (3). Watson + Crick + Franklin (1953) bakemuye iyi miterere bakoresheje X-ray crystallography. Iyo miterere yerekana uko DNA yikoporora kandi isomwa.",
      "replicate_unzip_copy_rezip": "Gukoporora — fungura, koporora, ongera ufunge",
      "helicase_splits_the_strands_dna_polyme": "Helicase itandukanya strand; DNA polymerase yubaka strand yuzuye. Semi-conservative — buri helix nshya ifite strand ishaje imwe + nshya imwe. Meselson na Stahl babyerekanye mu 1958.",
      "transcribe_dna_mrna_in_the_nucleus": "Kwandika — DNA → mRNA (mu nucleus)",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_one_dna_strand_3_": "RNA polymerase isoma DNA strand imwe 3′→5′ ikubaka RNA 5′→3′. Inyuguti ni zimwe, gusa T iba U. mRNA itwara amabwiriza kugeza ku ribosome — intambwe ya mbere ya central dogma.",
      "translate_mrna_protein_at_the_ribosome": "Guhindura — mRNA → protein (ku ribosome)",
      "64_codons_20_amino_acids_the_genetic_c": "codon 64 → amino acid 20 (genetic code irenze). AUG itangira; UAA/UAG/UGA zihagarika. tRNA isoma codon, izana amino acid nyayo, yubaka peptide bond.",
      "mutate_substitution_insertion_deletion": "Guhinduka — gusimbura, kwinjiza, gukuraho",
      "point_mutation_one_letter_swapped_inse": "Point mutation — inyuguti imwe yasimbuwe. Insertion/deletion — reading frame irimuka, protein yose yo hasi yangirika. Sickle cell anemia ni A→T imwe gusa — inyuguti imwe, ingaruka ku buzima bwose.",
      "crispr_the_precision_edit": "CRISPR — guhindura mu buryo bwuzuye",
      "bacterial_immune_system_repurposed_cas": "Sisitemu y'ubudahangarwa bwa bagiteri yakoreshejwe ku kindi. Cas9 enzyme + guide RNA = umukasi wa molekile. Doudna + Charpentier batsindiye Nobel 2020. CRISPR therapy ya mbere (sickle cell) FDA yayemeje muri Ukuboza 2023.",
      "protein_fold_function_malfunction": "Protein — guhina, umurimo, ikibazo",
      "sequence_determines_structure_determin": "Sequence igena structure igena umurimo. Hemoglobin itwara O₂, antibody irabimenya, enzyme ikora catalyze. AlphaFold (2020) yahanuye structure miliyoni 200 — ikibazo cy'imyaka 50 cyakemutse mu mezi 18.",
      "forensics_str_profiling_dna_evidence": "Siyansi y'ubutabera — STR profiling + ibimenyetso bya DNA",
      "codis_uses_20_short_tandem_repeat_str_": "CODIS ikoresha short tandem repeat (STR) loci 20. Amahirwe y'uko bihuza ari ay'igitangaza (rimwe kuri quadrillion) igihe loci zose zihuza. Innocence Project — ibihano birenga 245 by'amakosa byavanyweho nyuma yo gupima DNA.",
      "challenge_graded_problems": "Igerageza — ibibazo bihabwa amanota",
      "practice_transcription_translation_mut": "Toza transcription, translation, gutandukanya mutation. AP Bio Big Idea 3.A.1 — DNA (rimwe na rimwe RNA) ni ishingiro ryo gutanga amakuru y'irondakoko. NGSS HS-LS3-1.",
      "battle_head_to_head_retrieval": "Urugamba — kubona amaso ku maso",
      "retrieval_practice_gamified_speed_buil": "Kwitoza kubona — mu buryo bw'umukino. Umuvuduko wubaka automaticity — igihe kureba codon table bihinduka gukorwa byonyine, working memory yawe iba yisanzuye ku bitekerezo byo hejuru, nk'uguhanura ingaruka za mutation.",
      "learn_the_central_dogma_history": "Iga — central dogma + amateka",
      "dna_rna_protein_with_retroviruses_hiv_": "DNA → RNA → protein — hamwe na retrovirus (HIV) isubira inyuma na reverse transcriptase. Crick yahimbye ijambo \"dogma\" mu 1957; nyuma avuga risobanura igitekerezo, atari ukuri budahangarwa.",
      "build_a_dna_strand": "Ubaka DNA strand",
      "pick_a_sequence_the_complementary_stra": "Hitamo sequence — strand yuzuza yuzuzwa na base pairing (A-T, G-C). DNA nyayo yubakwa gutya buri gihe.",
      "dna_replication": "DNA replication",
      "helicase_unwinds_the_helix_dna_polymer": "Helicase ifungura helix; DNA polymerase isoma buri template strand ikubaka uzuzuza. Semi-conservative — buri daughter strand ifite ishaje imwe + nshya imwe.",
      "transcription_dna_mrna": "Transcription — DNA → mRNA",
      "rna_polymerase_reads_the_template_stra": "RNA polymerase isoma template strand. Amategeko amwe ya complementarity, ariko T → U. Igisubizo — mRNA copy imwe ya single-strand, yiteguye gusohoka mu nucleus.",
      "translation_mrna_protein": "Translation — mRNA → protein",
      "ribosome_reads_codons_3_bases_at_a_tim": "Ribosome isoma codon (base 3 icyarimwe). buri codon → amino acid imwe. Genetic code isomwa nka triplet itariho kwisumbuka, itariho akitso.",
      "mutations": "Mutation",
      "point_mutations_silent_no_protein_chan": "Point mutation — silent (protein ntihinduka), missense (amino acid itandukanye), nonsense (guhagarara hakiri kare). Frameshift (insertion/deletion) akenshi irangiza byose.",
      "crispr_cas9_editing": "CRISPR-Cas9 editing",
      "guide_rna_points_cas9_to_a_20_base_tar": "Guide RNA yerekeza Cas9 kuri target ya 20-base. Cas9 ica strand zombi. Repair pathway z'akagingo zifunga gene cyangwa zongeraho template watanze.",
      "protein_structure": "Structure ya protein",
      "primary_sequence_secondary_helix_sheet": "Primary (sequence) → secondary (α-helix, β-sheet) → tertiary (guhina 3D) → quaternary (multi-subunit). Guhindura amino acid imwe bishobora kwangiza guhina.",
      "dna_forensics": "DNA forensics",
      "str_profiling_13_20_short_tandem_repea": "STR profiling — short tandem repeat loci 13-20. Amahirwe y'uko bihuza ku bw'impanuka muri loci zose ni nka rimwe kuri miliyari. Ikoreshwa muri CODIS, paternity test, na forensic lab.",
      "daily_challenge": "Igerageza rya buri munsi",
      "a_new_dna_puzzle_every_session_transla": "Puzzle ya DNA nshya buri session. Hindura, menya mutation, shakisha ORF cyangwa kemura urubanza rwa forensic. Streak counter ikurikirana intsinzi ya buri munsi.",
      "codon_battle": "Codon battle",
      "speed_translation_duel_decode_codons_f": "Igerageza ry'umuvuduko ryo guhindura. Decode codon vuba urwana n'isaha. Gerageza niba genetic code iri mu mutwe wawe, atari ku reference card gusa.",
