      "sing_into_the_mic_the_lab_tracks_frequ": "Ririmba muri mikorofoni; laboratwari ikurikirana frecwensi mu gihe nyacyo. Abaririmbyi batojwe babika ubuhagarike mu ±5 cents (1/20 by'ijwi rya hagati) — uku ni ko ubuhagarike bwuzuye bwumvikana.",
