      "most_untrained_voices_span_1_5_2_octav": "Amajwi menshi atatojwe akwira octave 1.5-2; abaririmbyi ba kera batojwe bagera kuri 3 cyangwa hejuru. Kwagura urwego ahanini ni ukuvanga ba-rejistre, atari gukururira hejuru na hasi gusa.",
      "vibrato_lab_2": "Laboratwari ya Vibrato",
      "healthy_vibrato_5_7_hz_oscillation_60_": "Vibrato nzima: kunyeganyega kwa 5-7 Hz, kufite ubugari bwa ~60-100 cents. Buhoro cyane = kunyeganyega; byihuta cyane = guhinda. Vibrato ni umurimo w'inkunga y'umwuka yoroheye, atari ubuhanga bwihariye.",
