      "major_3rd_vs_minor_3rd_is_the_single_m": "Uwa gatatu munini na uwa gatatu muto ni ababiri b'intera bahangayikishije cyane abatangira. Ibimenyetso byo kwibuka: uwa gatatu munini = \"Oh when the saints\", uwa gatatu muto = \"Greensleeves\". Bubaka ukumva bijyanye.",
      "lip_trills_sirens_before_any_sustained": "Kunyeganyega kw'iminwa + siyereni mbere yo kuririmba kose kurambye. Iminota 5-10 yo gushyushya ku mbaraga nke igabanya ibyago byo gukoresha imigozi y'ijwi cyane ku kigero cy'igice. Gusimbuka gushyushya ni impamvu ya nimero 1 y'ibikomere by'ijwi bishobora kwirindwa.",
      "sight_reading_2": "Gusoma Inyandiko",
      "solf_ge_do_re_mi_letter_names_for_sigh": "Solfège (do-re-mi) iruta amazina y'inyuguti mu gusoma inyandiko kuko uduce tw'amagambo dushyira mu kode isano y'intera, atari ibimenyetso by'ubuhagarike gusa. Do igenda iruta do ihamye ku muziki w'amajwi.",
      "resonance_lab_discover_your_vocal_tone": "Laboratwari y'Isubiramo ry'Amajwi — Menya Ibara ry'Ijwi Ryawe",
      "two_sliders_throat_openness_and_soft_p": "Ba-slider babiri — gufungura umuhogo no kuzamura ijuru ry'akanwa ryoroshye — bahurira mu bwiza bune bw'ibara ry'ijwi (bukungahaye, bwaka, bushyushye, bw'izuru). Nta manota, nta gushyira ahagaragara: gerageza, andika, kandi usobanure ibyo umenya.",
      "rich_open_lifted": "🎶 Bukungahaye (bufunguye + buzamuye)",
      "operatic_professional_tone_full_resona": "Ibara ry'ijwi rya opera / ry'umwuga. Isubiramo ryuzuye.",
      "bright_open_lowered": "✨ Bwaka (bufunguye + bwamanuye)",
      "forward_placement_pop_belt_style": "Gushyira imbere. Uburyo bwa pop / belting.",
      "warm_narrow_lifted": "🌅 Bushyushye (bufunganye + buzamuye)",
      "mellow_tone_choral_acoustic": "Ibara ry'ijwi ryoroshye. Ry'itsinda / akustike.",
      "nasal_narrow_lowered": "🐝 Bw'izuru (bufunganye + bwamanuye)",
      "tight_resonance_often_unintended": "Isubiramo rikaze. Akenshi bitagambiriwe.",
      "resonance_discovery": "🎙️ Kuvumbura Isubiramo ry'Amajwi",
      "sliders_for_throat_openness_soft_palat": "Ba-slider bo gufungura umuhogo, kuzamura ijuru ry'akanwa ryoroshye. Gutandukanya bihariye n'amabara 4 y'ijwi. Nta manota, nta gushyira ahagaragara.",
      "hypothesis_what_anatomical_adjustments": "Igitekerezo: Ni izihe mpinduka z'imiterere y'umubiri zitanga ibara ry'ijwi bukungahaye?",
