      "interior_angle_sum_n_2_180_for_any_n_s": "Igiteranyo cy'inguni zo mu nda = (n − 2) × 180° ku mpande-nyinshi zose z'impande n. Buri nguni yo hanze y'impande-nyinshi ISANZWE = 360°/n. Igiteranyo cy'inguni zo hanze buri gihe = 360°.",
