      "1_rad_180_57_296_1_180_0_01745_rad_1_g": "1 rad = 180/π ≈ 57.296°. 1° = π/180 ≈ 0.01745 rad. 1 gon = 0.9°. Mibaruzi myinshi ifite uburyo bwa dogere/radiyani — menya neza ko uri mu buryo bukwiye!",
