      "crease_pattern_3d": "Ishusho y'amakunja → 3D",
      "flat_sheet_can_fold_into_virtually_any": "Urupapuro rusanzuye rushobora gukunjwa muri hafi imiterere iyo ari yo yose ya 3D hamwe n'amakunja ahagije. Origami igezweho iragoye cyane.",
      "real_world_space_telescopes": "Isi nyayo: telesikopi z'ikirere",
      "james_webb_space_telescope_sunshield_f": "Ingabo-y'izuba ya James Webb Space Telescope yakunjwe mu kohereza (amahame ya origami), ifungurwa mu kirere.",
      "real_world_airbags": "Isi nyayo: airbag",
