      "miura_fold": "Ikunja rya Miura",
      "parallelogram_based_fold_lets_large_su": "Ikunja rishingiye ku gicaparalelo rituma ubuso bunini (paneli y'izuba) buboneka buva ku bwoko buto bw'ikurura rimwe.",
      "kirigami": "Kirigami",
      "cuts_allowed_in_addition_to_folds_used": "Incisi zemewe hiyongereyeho amakunja. Bikoreshwa mu bitabo bidasimbuka + ibyubatswe bya siyansi.",
      "parallel_lines_converge_to_vanishing_p": "Imirongo iteganye ihurira ku tudomo tw'ukuzimira. Akadomo 1 (kureba hasi mu muhanda), utudomo 2 (impinga y'inyubako), utudomo 3 (kureba hejuru mu munara).",
      "where_parallel_lines_appear_to_meet_on": "Aho imirongo iteganye igaragara ihurira ku murongo w'ikirere. Bigenwa n'aho urebera + icyerekezo cy'umurongo.",
      "horizontal_line_at_viewer_s_eye_height": "Umurongo utambitse ku burebure bw'ijisho ry'urebera. Utudomo twose tw'ukuzimira turi kuri wo (ku mirongo iteganye n'ubutaka).",
      "objects_pointing_at_viewer_appear_comp": "Ibintu byerekeza urebera bigaragara byegeranye. Gushushanya ukuboko kwerekeza urebera = imbogamizi.",
